---
Get the current page URL

Usage: bl url [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --headless  Hide browser window (visible by default)
  -v, --verbose   Enable debug logging
      --json      Output as JSON
  -h, --help      Print help

Examples:
  bl url
  # Prints: https://example.com
